                                        <div class="comment-area">
                                            <p><%= t('pages.users.blog.details.you_guys_have_put_so_much_work_effort_and_time_w', 'You guys have put so much work, effort, and time while designing this awesome theme I can see that passion when I incorporated it into my website.') %></p>
